parameters.text:
=You are a professional business invoice assistant.

Using the customer information below, generate professional invoice content.

Customer Name: {{$json.customerName}}
Customer Email: {{$json.customerEmail}}
Company Name: {{$json.companyName}}
Invoice Number: {{$json.invoiceNumber}}
Invoice Date: {{$json.invoiceDate}}
Service Description: {{$json.serviceDescription}}
Invoice Amount: ₹{{$json.amount}}
Additional Notes: {{$json.notes}}

Generate the following:

1. Professional invoice summary

2. Thank you note

3. Payment reminder

4. Professional email subject

5. Professional email body

Write the response in clean Markdown with clear headings.

parameters.jsCode:
const item = $input.first().json;

// Due Date (7 days after invoice date)
const invoiceDate = new Date(item.invoiceDate);

const dueDate = new Date(invoiceDate);

dueDate.setDate(dueDate.getDate() + 7);

const formattedDue =
dueDate.toISOString().split("T")[0];

const html = `
